Adds a full Pipeline view (🔗 Pipeline tab) alongside Daily/Week/Audit:
- 7-column Kanban: Inquiry → Tour Booked → Toured → Offer Made → Enrolled → Retained/Referred → Lost
- Lead cards with family name, child info, source tag, days-in-stage
- Drag-and-drop between stages with auto-logged transitions
- Stale lead highlighting (>14 days in stage, per SOP)
- Lead detail modal with all SOP fields (tour date/outcome, lost reason, etc.)
- Conversation log per lead (outgoing/incoming/note entries)
- Search bar filters leads across all stages
- 5 Weekly Numbers summary in toolbar (inquiries, booked, toured, offers, enrolled)
- Full Supabase sync — PIPELINE data persists alongside schedule state
- Contact count tracking (3-contact max rule from SOP)
